ADDITIONALLY, A QUAINT GUEST, CARRIAGE HOUSE WITH 2 BEDROOMS AND 2 BATHS ADDS VERSALTILITY TO THIS REMARKABLE ESTATE.  DON'T MISS THIS RARE OPPORTUNITY TO EXPERIENCE THE QUINTESSENTIAL RURAL LIFESTYLE.
